---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import '../styles/global.css';

const pageTitle = "About Map’s Tour Buses";
---

<BaseLayout pageTitle={pageTitle}>
  <p>
    Map’s Tour Buses provides safe, comfortable, and reliable charter bus transportation
    for groups traveling across Texas and into Mexico.
  </p>

  <p>
    Whether you're planning a day trip, a multi-day tour, or transportation for a special
    event, our goal is to make every journey smooth, stress-free, and enjoyable.
  </p>

  <p>
    We pride ourselves on professional service, well-maintained vehicles, and experienced
    drivers who know the roads and destinations throughout the region.
  </p>

  <p>Our services include:</p>

  <ul>
    <li>Charter bus tours throughout Texas</li>
    <li>Group transportation to destinations in Mexico</li>
    <li>Private tours for events, schools, and organizations</li>
    <li>Comfortable buses designed for long-distance travel</li>
  </ul>

  <p>
    At Map’s Tour Buses, we believe the journey should be just as enjoyable as the destination.
    We look forward to being a part of your next adventure.
  </p>
</BaseLayout>